nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Good afternoon       I hope this message finds you . I forgot to ask during my surgery , will they remove my port as well? I forgot to ask when I met with surgeon. I hope this is something that can be done. I have also faxed my Org1 paperwork, have your office received it? Please let me know so I can have it completed before my surgery MM/DD/YYYY.
